      "created_at": "2021-01-20T22:22:25.574Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m not really sure what\u2019s different between this and TR.</p>\n<p>The setting for 3s smoothing on/off might be something, but I don\u2019t notice much of a difference from the times I\u2019ve used TR and now using TD. Both the chart and difference between actual power and targeted power seem to be straightforward except in TR it shows the numbers right next to each other, while in TD they are slightly apart. Maybe the little bar and \u201cdot\u201d to show whether you\u2019re on target or not? \"</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9_2_690x431.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"scrY2LgW8tPdjOUDbzLKTlEAmQV\" width=\"690\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9_2_690x431.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/1X/c5a52f4e7363b09ced0aa22915003d9520af89a9_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">970\u00d7606 60.6 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div><br>\n<img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/1X/3fed0fb7c9511231be873